Name: Suspicious Golden Apple Pastry
Desc: A little dessert made from apples. Having been left be too long, the softened outer skin now hides yet softer innards, with a flavor far removed from your envisaging... Uh oh. Your mouth's getting stuck shut...
Effect: Increases all party members' ATK by 224 and CRIT Rate by 6% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
